{"tid":2244661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃店用瑞士阿爾卑斯山既水先可以避免鬥黃","createTime":"2020-10-15T15:48:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T01:36:08.000Z","uid":81236,"like":50,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5b807f1ef449acbf96787acbcced82062727307e","tid":2244661,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T15:48:32.000Z","msg":"唔好用iphone ，因為中國製<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好用samsung，雖然韓國製但有零件中國製<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好上網，因為啲基站有中國零件<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好用電，因為發電過程有用到中國原料<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食黃店都唔得，因為水係東江水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鬥黃，就係唔著唔買唔食唔返工唔飲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鬥黃，就係自己繼續用iphone飲東江水然後屌人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲鬥黃？中國人都用美帝iphone 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2568400b48bd6c14784622e136f3063732bf8b2f","tid":2244661,"uid":81236,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T15:50:09.000Z","msg":"黃店一定唔可以用電用水<br />\n<br />\n因為會有中國製<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c1bfa35dbd71a5226abd5ab7e79ad95d8659a4","tid":2244661,"uid":81236,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2568400b48bd6c14784622e136f3063732bf8b2f","tid":2244661,"uid":81236,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T15:50:09.000Z","msg":"黃店一定唔可以用電用水<br />\n<br />\n因為會有中國製<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T15:51:25.000Z","msg":"邊間黃店有用都要開個post屌屌佢暗藍先"},{"pid":"2624fa20a14dae770b661827bddc46c83bff1392","tid":2244661,"uid":81236,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T15:53:24.000Z","msg":"黃店唔比香港人有discount<br />\n<br />\n服務態度唔夠真誠（由個人決定）<br />\n<br />\n賣貴出面幾蚊，唔係最平<br />\n<br />\n都唔夠黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要開post屌"},{"pid":"732c63637c3ba35b46095db2e9e536e85ce0a90e","tid":2244661,"uid":81236,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T15:54:31.000Z","msg":"不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4e7080daee77c8428462b27c37c7d1ddc40aa1","tid":2244661,"uid":134206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T15:55:39.000Z","msg":"岩呀"},{"pid":"edb8531a112947a4527448ebdd4c649e62749415","tid":2244661,"uid":81236,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T15:58:00.000Z","msg":"黃店賣既一定要100%非中國製<br />\n<br />\n用外國材料，外國人整，外國空運黎<br />\n<br />\n空運架發機要外國製，機組人員唔可以有中國人<br />\n<br />\n唔係都可能係假黃<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發自五毛iphone<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb19fd04f0a8179548611a5ae006ce38beb5d278","tid":2244661,"uid":81657,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T16:00:05.000Z","msg":"揸車要俾錢運輸署續牌，係咪即係俾錢政府嚟打手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7000ec3c1690a9e46c762b22729e1f0fb134ebf","tid":2244661,"uid":35910,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T16:01:11.000Z","msg":"真係好撚小事...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e1d0dcd90f2434a266444d699539f995a8c6ab","tid":2244661,"uid":89608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T16:01:53.000Z","msg":"好多人仲未明白現況,<br />\n活係幻想中, 同幻想抗爭梗"},{"pid":"fd8aa40306d1d49b078a3e623326fb3a8ea4bd72","tid":2244661,"uid":167394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2624fa20a14dae770b661827bddc46c83bff1392","tid":2244661,"uid":81236,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T15:53:24.000Z","msg":"黃店唔比香港人有discount<br />\n<br />\n服務態度唔夠真誠（由個人決定）<br />\n<br />\n賣貴出面幾蚊，唔係最平<br />\n<br />\n都唔夠黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要開post屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T16:03:29.000Z","msg":"野食太普通 太少 太貴"},{"pid":"aeadba447b6f38caf8a646a9ffaf981e84c6b99c","tid":2244661,"uid":61396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2568400b48bd6c14784622e136f3063732bf8b2f","tid":2244661,"uid":81236,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T15:50:09.000Z","msg":"黃店一定唔可以用電用水<br />\n<br />\n因為會有中國製<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T16:04:24.000Z","msg":"個食客都唔黃<br />\n邊個無用東江水<br />\n飲過東江水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f484bee4dfa014256c1e2afcac7d0397de8321","tid":2244661,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T16:04:36.000Z","msg":"好食咪照食<br />\n又柒又難食理得你黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc09bc64346be9c726181bcd5fa33a03a6d4e84d","tid":2244661,"uid":238920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T16:05:09.000Z","msg":"班人潔癖到要100%正確先得架<br />\n我極其懷疑係d pr5毛搶高地引戰<br />\n邊有可能日日都有新舖屌?<br />\n初期唔係話咩扮黃都由佢,做大個餅既咩?"},{"pid":"4a71783e58e21d2c092fb37edac39e63a1120989","tid":2244661,"uid":179649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T16:08:21.000Z","msg":"係黃網店買野食，收到先知係支國製<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但都有再幫襯<br />\n因為知佢地身體力行支持同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以就無所謂啦<br />\n其實好少事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n買鞋個post, 如果係我，只要係正版隻眼開隻眼閉算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最多咪無下次<br />\n但假野就要佢退錢"},{"pid":"4172d962012d6fc6f78875be4135ef6cfe1446f0","tid":2244661,"uid":84176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T16:12:28.000Z","msg":"唔係支那製都唔得<br />\nNew Balance去支那設廠，即係奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc749524aeb9810bf4a71c69be72965c34d8c25","tid":2244661,"uid":357710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2568400b48bd6c14784622e136f3063732bf8b2f","tid":2244661,"uid":81236,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T15:50:09.000Z","msg":"黃店一定唔可以用電用水<br />\n<br />\n因為會有中國製<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T16:46:08.000Z","msg":"阿共&nbsp;:&nbsp;我就同連登仔鬥黃由地底開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">構造</span><br />\n黃店腳下泥土詳看基本法第七條<br />\n黃店鐵閘國產率高達九成<br />\n黃店四邊和天花板石屎牆都是用國產水泥蓋的<br />\n黃店裝修材料國產率高達八成<br />\n黃店天空由我基本法18條富乳解放軍機自出自入,&nbsp;鬥黃者不得干涉<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">水電/食物資源</span><br />\n黃店70%國產東江水,&nbsp;剩下30%詳看基本法第七條<br />\n黃店30%國產大亞灣電(中電),&nbsp;20%國產東海天燃氣(港燈)<br />\n黃店使用國產餐具率高達九成<br />\n黃店使用國產蔬菜餐具率高達九成&nbsp;<br />\n黃店使用國產肉類高達三成<br />\n黃店內的空氣詳看基本法第七條<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">財政</span><br />\n黃店交租業主藍絲率高達八成&nbsp;<br />\n剩下二成黃店業主記得準時交地稅, 交差餉<br />\n黃店交管理費給藍絲管理公司率高達八成&nbsp;<br />\n黃店交佗地給藍絲黑社會率高達九成九&nbsp;<br />\n黃店收取中國銀行炒票率高達四成<br />\n黃店收銀聯/支付寶/微信其中一樣高達四成<br />\n黃店收八達通高達八成,&nbsp;而八達通公司90%股權屬黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n連登仔,&nbsp;問你服未?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a4f4d20731bce2176eeb749b1206aeb08fda624","tid":2244661,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T19:22:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2244825/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2244825/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n睇清楚兩黨同左媒形勢，就應該做實事, 背水一戰"},{"pid":"83525e918b29c54d5b4d6ac83754ba92f4bb13da","tid":2244661,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T19:37:14.000Z","msg":"論打擊黃圈最深、傷害黃圈最多嚟講，<br />\n黃圈最大的敵人根本就係黃絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce4c65968c15d89ac9c9f29add9a20dc089a9e5","tid":2244661,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T19:41:05.000Z","msg":"但黃字都係源於中國<br />\n點駁？"},{"pid":"6872a301ccabd7c046e228179cf76a2082133498","tid":2244661,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7000ec3c1690a9e46c762b22729e1f0fb134ebf","tid":2244661,"uid":35910,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T16:01:11.000Z","msg":"真係好撚小事...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T19:54:52.000Z","msg":"⋯⋯賣得唔夠平/明顯貴已經會有人屌XX係黑店，特別係食肆。其實黃店要求應該好低，佢敢擺明門口就話你知黃，就算係黑店都應該接受，不過就唔幫襯咁話，等佢自然淘汰。<br />\n<br />\n永冇可能唔批鬥對家，之後對願意自稱同一陣線嘅就成個奶奶咁左唔得右唔得。"},{"pid":"83265eb5f55272db18c8bd9e9475d4830e825282","tid":2244661,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T20:33:28.000Z","msg":"無需要潔癖<br />\n訂落黎既準則, 要極大部份人跟到至得<br />\n好多因為便利性同價錢 好難杯葛<br />\n比如麥當勞, 明知大部份人會跟唔到, 咁就唔需要杯葛<br />\n咁只會搞到條界線模糊左, 損自己士氣<br />\n高檔少少既餐廳, 較易搵到替代 利潤又高, 更值得針對性杯葛<br />\n所以杯葛要有針對性, 只大力推, 功能性易搵到替代品, 唔會犧牲便利性, 價錢接近, 既牌子產品黎杯葛"},{"pid":"1d76cd424d20adf25aeaa5473b74667960b95084","tid":2244661,"uid":167394,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"83525e918b29c54d5b4d6ac83754ba92f4bb13da","tid":2244661,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T19:37:14.000Z","msg":"論打擊黃圈最深、傷害黃圈最多嚟講，<br />\n黃圈最大的敵人根本就係黃絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T22:51:33.000Z","msg":"真黃定5毛"},{"pid":"c3ea9f513975f4f7c9fde9188d9b45c7b556becc","tid":2244661,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T01:26:47.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e9f5e05e30af24f8cd503483053f5384f9ec50","tid":2244661,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike